text: This charming ranch has been lovingly cared for by one owner, is located on a beautiful lot with a huge fenced backyard and is literally across the street from Butcher Park. Step onto the covered front porch and into the foyer and you will be greeted with a light-filled living room. Just steps away is the dining area which is open to the kitchen. A sliding door from the dining room opens into an expansive enclosed porch, perfect for summer evenings! A half bath is conveniently located off the kitchen. Three bedrooms and a full bathroom (with beautlfully maintained original tile!) finish off the first floor. It is believed hardwood flooring is beneath the carpet! Take a step back in time with this amazing finished basement complete with large recreation area, wet bar and gas fireplace. A large fenced backyard has a built-in gas grill, huge shade tree and shed for extra storage! Conveniently located to major road ways, shopping and restaurants, this home has it all! Make it yours today!

text: Warren: A vibrant town of many modest 3 bedroom MCM (mid century modern) brick ranch homes. Yet, not all are the same. Built in 1965 -- 28141 Liberty is 1, 376 s.f.!! Step inside the FOYER and you'll be greeted by HARD WOOD FLOORS, Coved Ceiling, & 1/2 Walls in the Living Room. To the right: Kitchen with beautiful MAPLE CABINETRY, enviable bank of drawers, striking dark Counters and Appliances, neutral Vinyl Flooring, soffits, & spacious Dining Area. The FAMILY ROOM is the star! Room to spread out, FIREPLACE, Doorwall to COVERED PATIO & expansive, FENCED BACK YARD, & SHED. Tucked away off the small hallway you'll find the UPDATED 1/2 BATH (on the 1st Floor.) For 1965, the 3 Bedrooms were well thought out. Wider Hallway, Larger Rooms & Closets & Hard Wood Floors. Light & Bright UPDATED FULL BATH has FULL WHITE VANITY (storage), DOUBLE SINKS, Neutral Ceramic & Glass Tile (to ceiling) in Tub area. BASEMENT is PARTIALLY FINISHED. Great for living space, or storage. COPPER PLUMBING, BREAKERS. GARAGE is FINISHED including ceiling where PULL DOWN STAIRS for ATTIC STORAGE are located. Taxes are Non-Homestead. Make 28141 Liberty Drive in Warren your HOME! B.A.T.V.A.I.

text: Welcome home to this lovingly maintained brick ranch, beautifully landscaped on a quiet, tree-lined street in Northwest Warren with Warren Consolidated Schools. Just under 1, 200 square feet on the entry level, but lives larger, offering surprisingly spacious rooms throughout. The living room features hardwood flooring under the carpet and a large picture window to bring in the light, and flows nicely into the kitchen area, which also includes dining space. Kitchen opens into a generous and carpeted family room which offers access to a cheerful 20x10 three season room. As you sit in the three-season room and sip your favorite beverage, you can enjoy the view of the lovely and private, fenced yard. All three bedrooms feature hardwood floors while the full hall bath includes a tiled floor, double sinks and tub with overhead shower. Finished lower level offers an additional 600 square feet of living space, including a kitchenette with additional sink and refrigerator, a half bath, pantry, storage cabinets, and glass block windows. A cheery laundry room completes the space. Detached two car garage has electricity and the shed offers the convenience of additional storage. This sweet home is a must see!

text: In a nutshell: not a typical Warren ranch. Must see to appreciate numerous updates & unique craftsmanship t/o this full-brick ranch set on almost 1/2 acre lot. Plus, 2024 built, SUPER SIZE (33'x25') garage w/8' h x 16'w garage door; side motor mounted opener; 10 ft ceiling, lighting and prepped for heat (pellet stove excluded). This move in ready, 1-story ranch home features spacious living room w/hardwood floors open to expanded kitchen with newer cabinets, under cab lighting & custom designed, STUNNING concrete counter tops. The 7 ft center island makes for easy dining & ultimate entertaining buffet. Newer SS appliances blend beautifully w/newer porcelain tile floor. Split floor plan features a HUGE primary bedroom w/double closet w/convenient and updated full bath just steps away. Opposite end of the home, you'll find 2 spacious bedrooms w/hardwood floors, large closets and 2nd full bath. Plus, an AWESOME dedicated laundry room w/newer washer & dryer, SS utility sink, storage closet and cabinets. Newer 18' x 32' newer Cedar deck is ready for you to enjoy! Plus, newer roof 2018; Newer vinyl windows: back of home 2023; 2020 boiler heating system & tankless water heater installed. Newer electrical receptacles, lighting & toggles installed t/o. Great curb appeal: circular drive, updated landscaping and ready for you! All potential buyer(s) must be accompanied by a licensed agent at all showings, inspections & walk thru. No virtual showings. Email offer package in 1 PDF format: include agency disclosure, pre-approval letter w/lender cell phone #, or current POF, PA/offer, signed disclosures. Seller prefers 3% EMD; prefer buyer(s) to avoid a split closing for various reasons. Seller will be using Embassy Title Agency for owner's policy & closing. See agent remarks for contact info. Please allow MINIMUM 48 HOURS for review of offer w/Seller. EXCLUSIONS listed in Agent Remarks. Please 2 hours notice to show. Thank you for showing!

text: This solid brick ranch has been well-maintained, is loaded with charm and updates, and is perfectly situated in the heart of a quiet, friendly neighborhood. The entry opens to a spacious living room with an abundance of natural light. Hardwood flooring present under carpet! The kitchen features numerous cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ceramic flooring. The kitchen is adjacent to an inviting dining space, plus a doorwall to the large three-season room overlooking the spacious backyard, where youll love spending time, enjoying the fresh air and sunshine! All of the bedrooms are amply sized with good closet space. The updated full bathroom features a granite vanity and a large tiled shower. Rounding out the main level is a convenient half bath located near the access to the oversized two-car garage. The full basement is clean, offering a workshop space, an additional hobby room, laundry facilities, and ample storage. A fabulous opportunity to create an extra living area if needed. The backyard features a generous paver patio, which, along with the three-season room, makes a substantial outdoor living area. The backyard is well-maintained and fenced. Mechanical updates include the furnace in 2011 and the new roof in 2013. Super close to Hartsig and Butcher parks and more community amenities. Warren Con schools with Siersma Elementary, Beer Middle, and Warren Mott High School. More features in docs!

text: Welcome to this beautifully updated ranch in the heart of Warren, Michigan! This turnkey home features a newer roof on both the house and garage (2023), updated electrical throughout, and has passed all city inspections for plumbing, electrical, HVAC, and zoningfully certified and ready to go as a rental if desired. Boasting over 2, 500 sq ft of finished space, the home offers three bedrooms on the main level, a living room, family room, and a rear addition with a stunning 15x23 bonus room featuring cathedral ceilings and new window blinds. The finished basement includes two large rooms (approximately 23x11 and 19x10), a potential fourth bedroom or office with a huge closet, and a mini kitchen area with cabinets, a sink, and a second new refrigerator. The laundry room is separate and includes a new washer and dryer. Additional updates include a new refrigerator and dishwasher in the main kitchen, beautiful flooring throughout, extra closet space, and an oversized garage. Just a short walk to the park this certified and move-in-ready home has it all!

This move-in-ready home blends comfort, style, and opportunity in a welcoming community.

text: Charming Kramer-built brick ranch located conveniently to all shops, restaurants and businesses yet perfectly situated in a mini cul-de-sac street. One of the last 3 original built in the Canterbury Heights neighborhood to sell. Once you enter you see a quiet family friendly neighborhood that is ideal to raise a family or begin to put down roots in the area. Excellent value of a home with original owner who has put in newer Anderson windows, newer roof (2021), newer HWT (2021), new HVAC system, less than 10 years old. Ample space 1, 615 above ground with 3 separate eating/living areas, full bath with hallway access and access bars for bath, 1st floor laundry, fully finished basement with bar/serving area which is great for entertaining parties. Attached 2 car garage with storage areas and epoxy flooring facing front of road for easy access in and out. The yard has plenty of mature trees and bushes keeping the home shaded during hot day. Backyard has 2 tiered deck with pergola and large area which can be fenced also with crabapple trees and functional sprinkler system to provide your own little oasis. Add separate water lines to allow for efficient use of water to the home. In short -- this home is a great value and will not last long. Come and See!

text: Welcome to 3393 Kevin Circle - a beautiful home nestled at the end of a quiet culdesac in Warren, offering comfort, privacy, and space for the whole family. Inside, you'll find a bright, open layout with vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace that create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious kitchen flows seamlessly into the living area, making it ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. Enjoy summer days in the fully fenced backyard complete with a underground sprinkling system, or relax on the porch with its convenient retractable sun shade. Live life worry free, this home has a generator too! Plus a large, full basement offers plenty of room for storage or future expansion. This charming home truly has it all - comfort, character, and a great location!

text: Multiple offers received, offer deadline Monday 8/11, 11 AM This charming brick ranch offers 3 bedrooms and 2.1 bathrooms, perfectly situated on a quiet, low-traffic street. With inviting curb appeal and a welcoming covered porch, this home is both warm and functional. Step inside to discover hardwood floors throughout and a bright living room with large windows that fill the space with natural light. The eat-in kitchen features a cozy breakfast nook, ample cabinet space, and sliding glass doors leading to the spacious fenced backyardcomplete with a patio and a beautiful mature tree providing shade. The main level hosts three comfortable bedrooms, a full bathroom with a dual-sink vanity, and a convenient half bath. Downstairs, the finished basement expands your living space with a bar area with a mini fridge, laundry room, additional storage. text: Fully updated and move-in ready, this 1807 sq ft brick ranch is nestled on a quiet street and showcases modern style with thoughtful updates throughout. The open-concept great room and kitchen feature vaulted ceilings, beautiful chandeliers, a natural fireplace, newly installed recessed lighting, and Pella windows with built-in blinds. The spacious kitchen offers quartz countertops, a marble backsplash, updated appliances, and an extra-deep breakfast bar, perfect for everyday living or entertaining. Luxury laminate flooring runs seamlessly throughout (installed in 2019), and the kitchen, bathrooms, and laundry room were remodeled in 2020. The home includes three generously sized bedrooms, including an oversized master suite with a walk-in closet, an additional large closet, and a stylish walk-in shower. The main-floor laundry and mudroom connect directly to the clean and spacious garage and a full-size 1807 sq ft basement with rough-in plumbingready for your finishing touches. Step outside to a private backyard with no rear neighbors, a freshly stained deck, and a 6-ft wood privacy fence with cedar cap (2020). Additional highlights include a newer furnace, A/C, and water heater (2018), a generator inlet box (2024), smart systems for the thermostat, door lock, and underground sprinklers, and vinyl siding with a lifetime warranty. Easement located at the rear of the yard (see survey). Some exclusions apply; please see agent remarks for details. This beautifully maintained home is ready to welcome your personal touch!

text: This fully remodeled 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home combines modern style with everyday comfort, featuring rich hardwood floors throughout the lower level and elegant porcelain tile in the kitchen and bathrooms. The updated kitchen has granite countertops and comes complete with all appliances, while both bathrooms have been upgraded. A partially finished basement with a full bath offers flexible living space perfect for a rec room. Major updates include a brand new HVAC system, AC, and roof all installed in 2023 providing peace of mind and energy efficiency for years to come. With high quality finishes and thoughtful upgrades throughout, this home is move in ready.

Charming 3-Bedroom Bungalow on a Double Lot! Welcome to this comfortable and well-maintained bungalow situated on two parcels (12-13-16-230-013 & 12-13-16-230-014) with a spacious 2-car garage. This home features a remodeled kitchen (2015), newer hot water heater (2016), and all new PVC plumbing from the house to the street (2015) for added peace of mind. Enjoy stylish wood laminate flooring throughout the first floor and a master bedroom complete with a walk-in closet. Additional highlights include glass block basement windows, updated circuit breakers (2015), and a newer furnace. The home showcases charming wet plaster walls with coved ceilings for added character. Appliances stay, along with upstairs window A/C unit. Located near Burdi Park and a residents-only dog park just around the cornerthis is a great place to call home!

text: Welcome to 8127 Continental, nestled in the heart of Warren! This beautifully updated home is designed with comfort and functionality in mind, featuring a spacious, light-filled layout and a warm, welcoming atmosphere. Recent updates throughout blend modern style with timeless charm, creating a space thats truly move-in ready. Start your mornings on the charming front porch or enjoy the generously sized living areas perfect for relaxing, entertaining, or working from home. Fresh finishes and neutral tones make it easy to personalize and call your own. The backyard offers a private setting ideal for gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding. Ideally located close to shopping, dining, parks, and major highways, youll enjoy both convenience and community. Welcome to 11400 Chicago Road in Warren, a hidden gem nestled on a sprawling 0.56-acre lot with a unique mid-century modern design that's full of potential! This 2, 029 square foot home offers a fantastic layout featuring an open floor plan that allows natural light to flow effortlessly throughout the main living areas. The first floor includes a primary bedroom with an en suite bathroom, a dedicated office space perfect for remote work or study, and the convenience of a first-floor laundry room. Upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom, providing plenty of space for family or guests. The home also includes an extra-deep basement thats ideal for storage or could be transformed into a fantastic bonus living space. Though the home needs some TLC, it boasts strong bones and endless opportunities for customization. For the savvy homeowner who is ready to put your personal touch on a one-of-a-kind property, this home is a must-see. The large lot provides plenty of room for outdoor entertaining, gardening, or expansion, while the location offers quick access to local amenities, shopping, schools, and more. text: Welcome home to this beautiful Warren bungalow on nearly a 1/2 acre with fully fenced backyard! You don't see yards like this often in Warren. All appliances are included in the sale, and remaining furniture is negotiable. This is a perfect starter or family home, but also priced right if purchased and held as a rental investment!

Very affordable house.

Tucked deep into the subdivision and withing walking distance to Miller Park, Wilde Elementary, and Regina High School.

text: This charming ranch that's move-in ready & packed with features is perfectly located just south of Maple Lane Golf Course and minutes from the General Motors Tech Center, Warren Recreation Center, and an abundance of shopping and dining options, this beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath ranch offers comfort, convenience, and space for every lifestyle. Step inside to find a spacious and light-filled step-down living room with a large picture window that pours in natural light and connects seamlessly to the dining area and ideal for family dinners or entertaining guests. The updated kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a peninsula island for extra prep space, and a cozy breakfast nook for everyday meals. The inviting family room is the perfect spot to unwind, with a warm fireplace and open sightlines to the kitchenideal for movie nights or casual get-togethers. Just off the kitchen, youll find a first-floor laundry room that doubles as a functional mudroom, conveniently located between the garage and basement entry. The private owners suite includes its own attached full bath, creating a peaceful retreat. Two additional generously sized bedrooms share a second full bathroom, offering flexibility for family or guests. The finished basement expands your living space and includes a bar area for entertaining, a large recreation/media room, and a flex space perfect for a home gym or game nights. A separate storage/mechanical room keeps everything organized and tucked away. Other highlights include an attached 2-car garage, a covered front porch for year-round use or to keep those delivered packages dry, plus a newer back patio and privacy fence for entertaining friends & family that's accented with mature trees providing natural shade and seclusion. With its prime location, thoughtful layout, and fantastic amenities, this home wont last long. NEW ROOF APRIL 2025. Schedule your showing today and make this ranch your new retreat now!

text: Open-concept all-brick ranch home features three (3) bedrooms and a living room, both with hardwood flooring. The family room includes a natural fireplace and luxury vinyl plank flooring installed in September 2024. The kitchen boasts ceramic tile, a brand-new quartz countertop, and a Delta faucet, along with a new garbage disposal, both installed in June 2025. Most walls are freshly painted, with recessed lighting and attic insulation added in 2021. Few other features include fenced backyard, a covered front porch, an insulated two-car attached garage with new motor system, a newly stained deck, and a newer roof (2015) with a complete tear-off. The full bathroom has been completely remodeled in June 2025, and a new furnace was installed two years ago. The hardwood floors, ceramic tile floors, and luxury vinyl plank floors make cleaning more efficient and quicker. Conveniently located near Pinewood Elementary and just two blocks from LaSalle High School, the home is also minutes from I-696, making it an ideal location for anyone.

Charming and Well-Maintained Brick Ranch in a Desirable Neighborhood This beautifully cared for three-bedroom, one-and-a-half-bath brick ranch offers a spacious and thoughtfully designed layout. The inviting living room features a large picture window that fills the space with natural light, and hardwood floors extend throughout the main level. Two of the bedrooms include double closets, and additional storage is available with dedicated hall and linen closets. The home is equipped with central air conditioning, vinyl windows. The full finished basement provides exceptional additional living space, including a generous 30 by 25 recreation room, a built-in bar, a bonus room suitable for an office or guest room, and abundant storage areas. A detached two-car garage sits adjacent to a large backyard that is perfect for outdoor enjoyment. The yard features a three-season room, a bonus shed located behind the garage, a pond, a paved walkway, and professional landscaping. An in-ground sprinkler system is also included to keep the grounds looking their best. All appliances are included with the home. This is a must-see property that combines comfort, functionality, and charm in a wonderful setting.

This stunning 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom single-family gem in a vibrant Warren neighborhood has been meticulously renovated to fuse modern luxury with cozy charm. Step inside to brand-new flooring throughout, fresh interior paint, and sleek contemporary finishes that create an inviting atmosphere from the start. The full bathroom dazzles with stylish ceramic tile flooring and modern fixtures, complemented by a convenient half-bath for daily practicality. The finished basement offers versatile space for a family room, home office, or entertainment hub. - this 1, 156 sq ft beauty sits on a spacious 55x148 lot (0.19 acres) with public sewer and water. Nestled in the heart of Warren, youre minutes from top schools, shopping, dining, and major expressways, making life effortless. This home is a lifestyle upgrade, blending low-maintenance living with enduring style. Has a City of Warren Residential Rental License that was issued in 2024 and valid until 3/25/2026, though if the new owner would like to use the property as a rental, they need to reapply for the license with the CIty of Warren. Dont miss this turnkey treasure in a thriving community. Schedule your private tour today and fall in love with every impeccable detail of this charming home!

text: Welcome Home!! With four bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home has plenty of space to grow, gather, and make your own. Several rooms have been completely repainted, and both bathrooms have been updated to feel fresh and modern. Smart outlets and light switches throughout allow for seamless control with Alexa or Google Home, making everyday life just a little easier. One of our favorite features is the heated and cooled 18x18 great room addition. We have used it as a creative studio for years, but it could easily be a cozy den, a playroom, or even a home office. The kitchen remains the heart of the home, with appliances that are just four years oldand theyll stay with the house. Major updates have already been taken care of, giving you peace of mind. The furnace and A/C were replaced just three years ago ($6, 000), and the roof was replaced at the same time ($14, 500). The basement stairs recently redone, making every part of the home feel fresh and well-maintained. Outside, the backyard has been a perfect retreat, with a large deck, space for pets to roam, and a fire pit for chilly evenings. Theres even a small roofed woodhouse to keep firewood dry and ready that stays. The two-car garage has been a lifesaver in winter, keeping the snow off our cars, but it also offers great storage or even potential for another functional space with a garage door screen enclosure everyone seems to be adding. Beyond the house itself, the neighborhood is truly something specialquiet, welcoming, and filled with wonderful neighbors. Just a few houses down, theres an in-home daycare, making this a great location for young families. This home has been a place of warmth and happiness, and were excited for someone new to make it their own. We hope youll love it as much as we have. all appliances included, 1 year home warranty, hardwood floors under the carpet upstairs, Warren Mott high school is a hop away, skip to the park and walk to shopping everything is so close to home. Freeway access to 696 or I-75 minutes away. BATVAI

text: Step into this charming 1940 bungalow in Warren and prepare to fall in lovethis 3 bedroom, 2 bath beauty has everything you need and hen some! The main floor greets you with stunning hardwood floors, a cozy living space (mounted tv is included!), a full bathroom and a bedroom perfect for guests, an office, or sneaking in a nap- perfect for those looking to avoid stairs. The kitchen has stone countertops and appliances are included. Upstairs, youll find two more spacious bedrooms, including one with a walk-in closet so big you might need a map, plus another full bath. Both bathrooms have quartz countertops and tubs to unwind in. Need extra space? The partially finished basement is ready for movie nights, a home gym, or that hobby you swore youd start. Previous owners had I beam system installed in 2022, AC and Anderson windows in 2020! Outside, the nearly half-acre lot is fully fenced and even includes a pad for a hot tub and a covered deck, offering plenty of room for backyard BBQs, pets, or even a garden that might (finally) survive (Includes adjacent lot parcel 1334158020). A 2-car garage keeps your cars (and you) out of Michigans unpredictable weather. To top it off, youre within walking distance of Lincoln Elementary, Middle, and High Schoolsso no more excuses for missing the bus! Dont waithomes like this dont stick around for long!

text: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with 2024 square feet living space situated on a desirable corner lot. This well-maintained property features a 2.5-detached garage and is equipped with modern updates, ensuring both comfort and efficiency. Inside, you'll find a newer high-efficiency furnace and air conditioner, along with newer windows in the lower level, making this home energy-efficient year-round. The home also features hardwood floors and solid doors. The attic insulation, installed 8 years ago, provides extra comfort and cost savings. The kitchen is equipped with stainless-steel appliances, including a refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, hood fan and microwave. The matching washer and dryer in the lower level were purchased 5 years ago. The lower level also features a partial kitchen, perfect for entertaining or additional living space. The garage roof is older, but the main house roof is newer.

text: This home is a Must See! New to market this home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and feels like country living in the City. A large 2187 sq ft. ranch with attached garage invites you to pull in and park, plus room for a circle drive if desired. Covered front porch for warm summer nights. The front door opens to a large foyer and living room with brand new carpeting. The entire home has just been painted. The dining area off of the kitchen is very large with Brazilian Cherry hardwoods thru to the kitchen area. The kitchen has been designer updated with granite countertops, large island, stainless steel appliances, GE Monogram and built-in Refrigerator and Freezer, with lots of beautiful wood cabinets. The four bedrooms are all good size with hardwood floors. The family room offers Parquet floors and gas fireplace with door wall leading to a patio. There is a first floor laundry. Just completed new roof installed 2025 and lots of other updates throughout. The rear yard is fenced offering a lot of privacy plus an additional 20 x 20 garage. BATVAI

text: Wonderful location, setting and opportunity to make this 3 bedroom 1 bath brick home your own. Great setting on a wide 60 x 126 yard provides ample outdoor recreation and gardening space. Ideal location just down the street from fabulous Westview Elementary School campus. Classic floor plan with proper vestibule entry. Big living room with newer carpeting. Hardwood floors believed to be beneath carpeting in all bedrooms, hall, dining and living rooms. Primary bedroom with spacious closet. Large updated ceramic tiled main bath with newer tub surround and fixtures. Dimensional shingled roof on house. Vinyl replacement windows. Bright kitchen with table space and LVP flooring. Finished lower level extends living space with big family room and half bath, plus unfinished storage areas with shelving. Full brick all sides house exterior with aluminum soffits and trim for low maintenance. Furnace just serviced and in excellent condition, central air, newer water heater, copper plumbing. Oversized 2 car garage and double wide driveway to park all your vehicles with plenty of storage and working space. Fenced yard to let the dog out with access from back hall. Great western Warren location with quick access to anywhere you need to go. You will love this neat well-kept home please take a look!

text: This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom bungalow offers both comfort and convenience, with easy access to major expressways and nearby amenities. Move right into this classic ranch on a quiet street in a great location. You will love the perfectly updated kitchen. A pass through to the living room opens the space and enhances light. The original wood floors have been refinished and are in great shape. Outdoors, enjoy the low maintenance brick paver patio. Children and pets can play in the fully fenced yard, don't miss the garden space! The furnace and electrical service were replaced in 2023. Welcome home! This fabulous NW Warren brick split-level has been remodeled from top to bottom! As you step inside the airy & inviting main level, youre greeted by the perfect blend of modern updates & functionality, starting with the the open layout and space-enhancing vaulted ceilings! The stunning kitchen boasts gorgeous two-tone cherry cabinetry, granite counters, stainless appliances, recessed lighting, & spacious dining area! Youll enjoy an abundance of counter space & storage, including a huge pantry! Just a few steps up are 3 generously-sized bedrooms (each with large closets), and the tastefully updated full bath! The lower level is equally impressive, offering a bright spacious family room, featuring luxury plank flooring & pallet wall accents! The newly remodeled half bath, and a separate laundry room tucked away also add convenience. And the huge storage room is a major plus! Easy walk-out access to the spacious backyard, which is fenced & beautifully landscaped, making it a private retreat! The large covered patio is perfect for outdoor entertaining, rain or shine! The 1.5 car detached garage allows parking and space for lawn equipment & toys too! Updates in recent years include carpet (2023), refinished hardwood floors (2022), Wallside windows, newer boiler system (2009), two energy-efficient cooling units professionally encased in windows (2018), electrical service & panel (2020), & roof professionally sealed with warranty (2024)! Prime location, near everything you want and & need, and just minutes from trendy downtown Detroit! This home is truly a must-see!

text: This home is far more than it looks!! The space is perfect for multigenerational families or kids moving back in from college! With 5 bedrooms and 3.5 baths , you have plenty of room for all. The main floor has 3 bedrooms, The master with a private en-suite, all hardwood floor recently brought back to life and beautiful! Step down into your vaulted and beamed living room with a fireplace for cozy family gatherings and just steps away an enclosed sunroom to relax in and enjoy your fenced in yard with irrigation system. The kitchen is open to below so the cook doesn't miss all the action. Upstairs you will find 2 additional bedrooms and large bathroom for kids or guests or even the grandparents to visit or stay with you! It doesn't stop there, the basement is finished for entertaining with bar or summer kitchen area. Don't forget sleepovers for the birthday parties and all the kids, so much room! an additional half bath and laundry area, plus more storage space or dads workshop. 2 furnaces and 2 central air units to control the different areas of the house too. So much space and potential for you to make it your own.

text: Calling Chip and Joanna! Rare opportunity to restore a charming historic .89 acre property on Red Run creek. Located in the Village of Warren, the Gillett- Beer farm dates to the 1830's. It is fronted by a main house with 2- 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, full basement, and attached 1 car garage. This homestead also includes a 1 bed 1 bath cottage, and a barn that predates the main house. Barn has multiple rooms and paned windows and was used from the 1940's on as an artist's studio. This is a great opportunity for those who are interested in restoring a historic property as well those attracted by a large piece of land in a bucolic setting.

text: Immaculate and lovingly cared for home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths (with basement plumbed and toilet installed ready to be finished!) This home sits in a cul de sac with a private tree lined yard. Enjoy the peacefulness in the attached sunroom with neutral ceramic tiled floor. Custom white shutters throughout with beautiful tongue and groove hardwood floors. Spacious living room with gas fireplace and vaulted ceilings. Private office/flex space with corner windows. Primary bedroom boast walk in closet and en suite bath with stand up shower. All 3 bedrooms complete with neutral wall and carpet colors. The huge basement is ready to be finished or use as is! There is a 2nd entrance in from the two car garage that leads directly to the basement stairs for ease of moving big items or possibly a private entrance for a resident. An extra large driveway with plenty of space for visitors or extra vehicles. Minutes away from Maple Lane Golf Club, convenient to shopping and the GM Tech Center. This home is the true definition of Turn Key . All appliances included as well as the custom dining room table that matches the countertop, glass shelving in the bedroom and living room tv and mount.

text: Home back on the market at no fault of its own. Welcome Home to 32677 Knapp Ave. This beautiful home is only 6 years old. As you enter the home your greeted by your open concept main living area with a nice sized living room and nice sized kitchen with island and your dining area. Heading down the hallway you have your first of two full baths. As you continue down the hallway there are two nice sized bedrooms. At the end of the hallway is your primary bedroom complete with ensuite bathroom and nice sized walk-in closet. As you head downstairs to your partially finished basement you have plenty of room for entertaining. The area currently setup with a bar could easily be converted to your 4th bedroom if needed. Also downstairs you will find your laundry room complete with utility sink. As you head outside you will find a nice sized fenced in backyard great for your four legged family members. Backyard also has a nice sized cement patio with bench seating and pergola, perfect for entertaining and showing off your BBQ Skills. Bates Park is across the street and from time to time you will see some wildlife roaming around. Home is close to lots of stores and restaurants and the GM Tech Center is just a few minutes away. Home has lots of new paint throughout, newer stove and new carpet in first bedroom. Buyers and Buyers Agent to confirm all information. Listing Agent is related to Seller. 2 Dressers, nightstand, round coffee table in living room, 2 tables and chairs along with bar stools in basement are being sold with home.
